## What Cline Should NOT Do

- Do not touch read-only files
- Do not add features beyond what the directive specifies
- Do not refactor code that isn't broken
- Do not add abstractions for single-use code
- Do not skip the pre-flight pytest check
- Do not claim completion without raw terminal proof
- Do not create files in `duggerbot/ralph/` without a Phase 4 directive
